      "writtenOn": "2020-06-30T21:56:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I find the naming of this function confusing. What\u0027s it detaching the buffers from? I\u0027m guessing \"staged\" is a new state? We used to have Busy, Available, Active. What are the new states, and do they correspond to the old ones at all?",
      "revId": "2c79e1f0850ca11c2bd56733f80694f54a0ca99e",
