      "message": "Seems a shame that we have a linked list, but can\u0027t remove in O(1) time. Did you consider using an SkInternalList instead? Then you wouldn\u0027t need a loop at all.",
      "revId": "2c79e1f0850ca11c2bd56733f80694f54a0ca99e",
